scene.message:
Yukino: Even as we stand here,{nl}
time keeps slipping by. It's{nl}
so frustrating.{waitkey}{clearbox}Really, it makes me feel like{nl}
maybe I'm powerless.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hey, how long do you{nl}
intend to stay in a place{nl}
like this?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The school ending up{nl}
like this is a real problem,{nl}
sure, but{waitkey}{clearbox}somehow it's like being freed{nl}
from boring everyday life —{nl}
kinda exciting, huh!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: The Tower of Thanatos,{nl}
Tartarus... it's practically{nl}
Greek mythology.{waitkey}{ret}
